posts.post_content:
Looking to trade these for non T206 cards (1912 or earlier).  Please submit offers to [url]esharpwork@gmail.com[/url]

Ames has the edge of another back on the right side showing.

Jenkins has been donated.  

Can't believe nobody has offered me any 1989 Topps yet.

Just want to give a big shoutout to Tao.  I have been working for a few months on accumulating and extra low-grade set of T210s to donate to my local history museum.  The Jenkins was the last one needed and I shipped him an offer. He responded that he would be delighted to give it to me. Very nice gesture!
